This is MALDIVES 🌴💦🐠

An unimaginable paradise of pristine beaches, crystal clear waters, bucket list hotels & marine encounters. 

TOP THINGS TO KNOW ⬇️

🏩 There are more than 170 hotels in Maldives! Book the best deals with @luxury.escapes

🌞 Best weather = Dec - April (minimal rain & beautiful sunny days!)

✈️ Take a seaplane ride - it’s a bucket list experience!

🪂 Try parasailing, the scenery is out of this world!

🦈 MUST DO: Swim with majestic nurse sharks, whale sharks & manta rays. 

🪸Coral reefs are very colourful & at most hotels you will be able to snorkel amongst thriving coral straight from the beach!

#partner

#worldplaces #exploremaldives #maldivesislands #maldivesresorts #worldtravel #bestviews

This is your sign to book a trip to Byron Bay, Australia 🇦🇺 🐨 

Don’t miss these must do experiences:

-Wategos Beach
-The Pass (my fav surf beach)
-Killen Falls
-Byron Bay Lighthouse
-Food: Treehouse, TopShop, High Life, Folk
-Bangalow + Newrybar (for cute shopping, antiques & flowers)
-Farmers Market (every Thursday)

Ps. all my shoes are by sustainable Hawaiian brand @olukai 🌺 (I’m never not wearing these & just a public service announcement, they just dropped a new collection which I’m wearing in this video 😍) #AnywhereAloha

#travelaustralia #australiatravel #visitaustralia #exploreaustralia #beautifullocation #travelbucketlist #byronbay

HERE are my must visit locations in Oman 🇴🇲

One of the most spectacular & mind blowing countries in the world. This is a trip I will NEVER forget - you have to add Oman to your travel bucketlist!

Must do:

🕌Visit the Grand Mosque in Muscat
💦Cool off in a Wadi (crystal clear natural pools)
🚐Go on a roadtrip (it’s completely safe!!)
🐠 Visit the protected islands of Dimaniyat
🏜️Go glamping in the Wahiba Sands desert
❤️Be blown away by the kindness of locals 🙏🏽
📜Don’t miss the ancient city of Nizwa (our fav)
🌴Eat dates, shop & drink coffee in the souls
🐪See wild camels in the desert
✨Experience Omans rich culture

Mexico’s TOP Hotels (Part 1) ⬇️

In my opinion Mexico is one of the most underrated countries in the world! It has so much to offer from food & culture to epic experiences, unreal landscapes & bucketlist hotels!

Add these 4 luxury hotels to your Mexico travel list & thank me later: 

💦 La Valise, Tulum
🌴 Careyes, Villa Destination, Costalegre
🌮 Four Seasons Tamarindo, Costalegre 
🌵Paradero, Todos Santos

Run away with me to Bora Bora 🫶🏽

Even after the many island & beach destinations I have been blessed to visit, French Polynesia is still one of the most beautiful places I have travelled. A living, breathing postcard (& even better in real life). The energy, people & their love of nature BUZZES here. For me, it feels like home!
